    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, it is a total gem! This beauty has been pampered since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously cared for, and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect in every way, you\u2019ve found it! I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy this spotless machine\u2014come see it for yourself!",
      "price": 48500.0,
