    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to show you this total gem. Honestly, it's in such incredible shape that you'd swear it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered its whole life and is looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. It drives like an absolute dream and is spotless inside and out. If you're looking for that perfect, like-new feel, you've definitely found it! Let's get you in for a test drive\u2014you're going to love it!",
